<doxygen xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="compound.xsd" version="1.14.0" xml:lang="en-US">
  <compounddef id="RESTORE" kind="page">
    <compoundname>RESTORE</compoundname>
    <title>RESTORE Keyword</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">RESTORE</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">RESTORE<sp/>offset</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Resets or repositions the current <computeroutput>DATA</computeroutput> read pointer.</para>
<para>With no argument, <computeroutput>RESTORE</computeroutput> resets the read position to the start of the program&apos;s data stream.</para>
<para>With an argument, <computeroutput>RESTORE</computeroutput> sets the read position to a specific zero-based <computeroutput>DATA</computeroutput> offset.</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<sect1 id="RESTORE_1example-18_1s1"><sect2 id="RESTORE_1example-18_1s2"><sect3 id="RESTORE_1example-18_1s3"><sect4 id="RESTORE_1example-18_1s4"><sect5 id="RESTORE_1example-18">
<title>Example</title><para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">DATA<sp/>10,<sp/>20</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">DATA<sp/>30</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>DATAREAD</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>DATAREAD</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">RESTORE</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>DATAREAD</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>This prints:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">10</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">20</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">10</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
</sect5></sect4></sect3></sect2></sect1>
<sect1 id="RESTORE_1example-with-offset_1s1"><sect2 id="RESTORE_1example-with-offset_1s2"><sect3 id="RESTORE_1example-with-offset_1s3"><sect4 id="RESTORE_1example-with-offset_1s4"><sect5 id="RESTORE_1example-with-offset">
<title>Example with offset</title><para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">DATA<sp/>10,<sp/>20,<sp/>30</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">RESTORE<sp/>1</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>DATAREAD</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>DATAREAD</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>This prints:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">20</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">30</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
</sect5></sect4></sect3></sect2></sect1>
<sect1 id="RESTORE_1behaviour-11_1s1"><sect2 id="RESTORE_1behaviour-11_1s2"><sect3 id="RESTORE_1behaviour-11_1s3"><sect4 id="RESTORE_1behaviour-11_1s4"><sect5 id="RESTORE_1behaviour-11">
<title>Behaviour</title><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>RESTORE</computeroutput> with no argument resets the data pointer to offset <computeroutput>0</computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>RESTORE N</computeroutput> moves the data pointer to offset <computeroutput>N</computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Offsets are zero-based.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>The offset refers to the internal position within the combined <computeroutput>DATA</computeroutput> stream, not to a line number.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>An invalid offset produces a runtime error.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>RESTORE</computeroutput> affects subsequent calls to <ref refid="DATAREAD" kindref="compound">DATAREAD</ref>, <ref refid="DATAREADR" kindref="compound">DATAREADR</ref>, and <ref refid="DATAREADS" kindref="compound">DATAREAD$</ref>.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
</sect5></sect4></sect3></sect2></sect1>
